KRAZYFISH GRILLE
/$
$
Enjoy lively music with a coastal-inspired menu and a fresh concept. We use locally sourced ingredients and make all of our wonderful dishes fresh daily.
We feel we have the best drink menu on the coast, so leave your worries at the door and soak in the carefree atmosphere that we strive hard to achieve. Eat some food, enjoy the Florida Sunshine, have a cool drink, and free your inner beach bum. Welcome.... Sit back, Relax, and Enjoy!
Mark Haddock
Founder
